CHƯƠNG 1: MÔ TẢ VỀ TẬP DỮ LIỆU¶

  1. Tp d liu "Adult Salary Prediction"
  • L mt tp d liu v thu nhp hng nm ca cc c nhn c ly t trang UCI, s dng d on thu nhp ca mt c nhn da trn cc thuc tnh nh tui, gii tnh, trnh hc vn, ngh nghip, s gi lm vic mt tun, quc gia. Tp d liu ny c s dng thc hin cc bi ton phn loi, iu tra mi quan h gia cc thuc tnh v thu nhp.
  • ng dn tp d liu: https://archive.ics.uci.edu/ml/datasets/adult
  • M t cc bin trong tp d liu:
    • age: Tui ca ngi i lm (dng s nguyn)
    • workclass: Hnh thc lm vic ca ngi i lm (dng chui). Cc gi tr c th l:
      • Private: Ngi ln lm vic cho mt t chc t nhn, cng ty hoc doanh nghip.
      • Self-emp-not-inc: Ngi ln lm vic t do, khng phi lm vic cho mt cng ty hoc t chc no.
      • Self-emp-inc: Ngi ln lm vic t do, nhng h l ch s hu ca mt cng ty hoc t chc.
      • Federal-gov: Ngi ln lm vic cho chnh ph lin bang ca Hoa K.
      • Local-gov: Ngi ln lm vic cho chnh quyn a phng.
      • Ngi ln lm vic cho chnh ph bang ca Hoa K.
      • Ngi ln khng nhn c lng hoc khng c vic lm hin ti.
      • Ngi ln cha bao gi c vic lm hoc khng c kinh nghim lm vic trc .
    • fnlwgt: Trng s c tnh ton da trn d liu iu tra dn s ca M nm 1994 (dng s nguyn).
    • education: Trnh hc vn ca ngi i lm (dng chui). Cc gi tr c th l:
      • Bachelors: C nhn (i hc)
      • Some-college: C mt s tn ch i hc nhng cha tt nghip
      • 11th: Lp 11 trung hc ph thng
      • HS-grad: Tt nghip trung hc ph thng (12 nm hc)
      • Prof-school: Trng chuyn nghip (chng hn nh trng lut, trng y t, trng kinh doanh)
      • Assoc-acdm: Tn ch hc vn ngh nghip hoc i hc (chng hn nh k thut vin hoc trung tm o to k nng)
      • Assoc-voc: Vn bng ngh nghip (chng hn nh k thut vin hoc k s chuyn mn)
      • 9th: Lp 9
      • 7th-8th: Lp 7 hoc 8
      • 12th: Lp 12
      • Masters: Thc s
      • 1st-4th: Lp 1 n lp 4
      • 10th: Lp 10 trung hc ph thng
      • Doctorate: Tin s
      • 5th-6th: Lp 5 hoc 6
      • Preschool: Mu gio
    • education_num: Trnh hc vn ca ngi i lm (di dng s nguyn).
    • marital_status: Tnh trng hn nhn ca ngi i lm (dng chui). Cc gi tr c th l:
      • Married-civ-spouse: kt hn vi mt cng dn (khng phi qun nhn)
      • Divorced: ly d
      • Never-married: Cha tng kt hn
      • Separated: chia tay nhng cha ly d
      • Widowed: mt v hoc chng
      • Married-spouse-absent: kt hn nhng v hoc chng hin khng c mt
      • Married-AF-spouse: kt hn vi mt qun nhn
    • occupation: Ngh nghip ca ngi i lm (dng chui). Cc gi tr c th l:
      • Tech-support: H tr k thut
      • Craft-repair: Sa cha, th th cng
      • Other-service: Dch v khc
      • Sales: Bn hng
      • Exec-managerial: Qun l i tc v iu hnh (ch tch, gim c iu hnh)
      • Prof-specialty: Chuyn mn chuyn nghip (chng hn nh bc s, lut s, k s)
      • Handlers-cleaners: Vn hnh v v sinh (chng hn nh nhn vin v sinh, nhn vin bc xp)
      • Machine-op-inspct: Vn hnh my mc v kim tra
      • Adm-clerical: Hnh chnh v vn phng (chng hn nh nhn vin hnh chnh, th k)
      • Farming-fishing: Nng nghip v nh bt c
      • Transport-moving: Vn chuyn v di chuyn (chng hn nh ti x, nhn vin kho vn)
      • Priv-house-serv: Dch v gia nh ring t (chng hn nh ngi gip vic gia nh)
      • Protective-serv: Bo v v an ninh (chng hn nh nhn vin bo v, cnh st)
      • Armed-Forces: Lc lng v trang
    • relationship: Mi quan h ca ngi i lm trong gia nh (dng chui). Cc gi tr c th l:
      • Wife: V
      • Own-child: Con ring
      • Husband: Chng
      • Not-in-family: Khng phi trong gia nh (chng hn nh bn b, ng nghip)
      • Other-relative: H hng khc
      • Unmarried: Cha kt hn hoc khng c i tc
    • race: Sc tc ca ngi ln (dng chui). Cc gi tr c th l:
      • White: Da trng
      • Asian-Pac-Islander: chu - Thi Bnh Dng - o quc s t (chng hn nh ngi Trung Quc, ngi Nht Bn, ngi Hn Quc, ngi Vit Nam)
      • Amer-Indian-Eskimo: Th dn M - Eskimo (chng hn nh ngi Da , ngi Eskimo)
      • Black: Da en
    • sex: Gii tnh ca ngi i lm (dng chui). Cc gi tr c th l:
      • Male: Nam
      • Female: N
    • capital_gain: Thu nhp t ti sn (dng s nguyn).
      • L thu nhp m mt ngi i lm thu c t vic bn ti sn (chng hn nh bt ng sn, chng khon, kinh doanh) vi gi cao hn so vi gi mua ban u. V d, nu mt ngi bn mt cn nh vi gi cao hn so vi gi mua ban u, th khon thu nhp thu c t bn nh chnh l "capital gain".
    • capital_loss: Chi ph t ti sn (dng s nguyn).
      • L chi ph m mt ngi ln phi chu khi bn ti sn vi gi thp hn so vi gi mua ban u. V d, nu mt ngi bn mt chng khon vi gi thp hn so vi gi mua ban u, th khon chi ph chnh l "capital loss".
    • hours_per_week: S gi lm vic mi tun (dng s nguyn).
    • native_country: Quc gia ca ngi i lm (dng chui).
    • income: Thu nhp ca ngi ln, c chia thnh hai lp: ">50K" v "<=50K" (dng chui).
  1. Tp d liu "Temperature Prediction"
  • Tp d liu "Temperature Prediction" cha thng tin lch s v thi tit xung quanh Szeged, Hungary trong khong thi gian t ngy 1/1/2006 n ngy 31/12/2016. Tp d liu ny c thu thp t cc trm thi tit trong khu vc v cha thng tin v cc ch s nh nhit , m, tc gi, p sut kh quyn, my v cm gic nhit.B d liu ny c th c s dng xy dng cc m hnh d on nhit da trn cc thng tin kh tng. Tp d liu ny dng xy dng cc m hnh d on nhit da trn cc thng tin kh tng.
  • ng dn tp d liu: https://www.kaggle.com/code/vivekanandbhardwaj/temperature-prediction/input
  • M t cc bin trong tp d liu:
    • Formatted Date: thi im o nhit (dng dd/mm/yyyy hh:mm:ss).
    • Summary: tnh trng thi tit trong ngy c ghi li(dng chui).
    • Precip Type: phn loi ma c ghi li, ma hoc tuyt.
    • Temperature (C): Nhit o tnh bng C.
    • Apparent Temperature (C): Nhit cm nhn c bng C.
    • Humidity: m c o theo phn trm.
    • Wind Speed (km/h): Tc gi km/h.
    • Wind Bearing (degrees): Hng gi o theo .
    • Visibility (km): Phm vi tm nhn trong n v km.
    • Loud Cover: Gi tr khng c.
    • Pressure (millibars): p sut kh quyn o bng n v millibars.
    • Daily Summary: Tnh hnh thi tit trong ngy.

CHƯƠNG 2: PHÂN TÍCH KỸ THUẬT ÁP DỤNG¶

  1. K thut hi quy tuyn tnh
  • u im:
    • Tp d liu c thu thp v t chc mt cch cn thn, gip cho vic x l v phn tch d dng hn.
    • Tp d liu c kch thc ln v cha nhiu thng tin a dng v nhit , m, tc gi v p sut. iu ny cho php m hnh hc c mi quan h phc tp gia cc bin u vo v bin mc tiu.
    • Tp d liu khng c gi tr thiu: iu ny gip cho vic xy dng cc m hnh c t sai s, ng thi gip tit kim thi gian trong vic xy dng cc mn hnh cu vic khai ph d liu.
    • Cc bin u vo c mi quan h tuyn tnh: Nh hnh m t tp d liu tng qut ban u pha trn th cc bin trong tp d liu c quan h tuyn tnh m m hnh Linear Regression li gi nh mi quan h tuyn tnh gia bin u vo v bin mc tiu nn khi p dng m hnh vo tp d liu th cc k ph hp.
  • Nhc im:
    • C th c s tng quan khng hon ho: Trong tp d liu thc t, c th c nhng mi quan h phi tuyn hoc tng quan khng hon ho gia cc bin, dn n m hnh Linear Regression khng th m phng ng mi quan h gia cc bin trong tp d liu
    • Tp d liu c th thiu mt s bin quan trng khc c th nh hng n bin mc tiu nh ma, v tr a l, hay cc yu t khc.
  1. K thut Support Vector Machine
  • u im:
    • Hiu sut cao: SVM c kh nng x l hiu qu cc tp d liu ln v phc tp. Thut ton c th xy dng cc siu phng tt phn loi cc lp d liu.
    • Hiu qu trong khng gian chiu cao: SVM c kh nng x l d liu c s chiu cao m khng gp vn v vic tng ng k chi ph tnh ton.
    • tin cy cao: SVM xy dng cc siu phng ti u phn loi d liu v m bo gii hn sai s.
    • Tnh linh hot: SVM h tr s dng cc hm kernel phn loi d liu phi tuyn.
  • Nhc im:
    • phc tp tnh ton: Trong mt s trng hp, vic hun luyn m hnh SVM c th tn nhiu thi gian v ti nguyn tnh ton.
    • Nhy cm vi nhiu: SVM c th b nh hng bi nhiu trong d liu v d dn n overfitting nu khng c iu chnh ng.
    • Kh khn trong vic chn siu tham s: Vic tinh chnh cc siu tham s ca SVM nh hm kernel, rng buc v thng s iu chnh n by l mt thch thc v yu cu kin thc v kinh nghim.
  1. K thut RandomForest
  • u im:
    • M hnh c chnh xc cao: Random Forest c coi l mt trong nhng m hnh phn loi v d on tt nht trong machine learning v n c kh nng gim overfitting v cung cp chnh xc cao.
    • Kh nng x l tp d liu ln: Random Forest c th x l tp d liu ln, c s lng c trng ln v gii quyt cc vn v ph thuc tuyn tnh.
    • Kh nng x l cc c trng b khuyt d liu: Random Forest c th x l cc c trng b khuyt d liu m khng cn loi b chng.
    • Kh nng xc nh c trng quan trng: Random Forest c th nh gi quan trng ca cc c trng v xc nh c trng quan trng trong vic phn loi v d on.
    • Kh nng x l nhiu: Random Forest c kh nng x l nhiu v gim thiu nh hng ca d liu nhiu.
  • Nhc im:
    • i hi thi gian v ti nguyn tnh ton: Random Forest c th yu cu nhiu thi gian v ti nguyn tnh ton xy dng v o to m hnh.
    • Khng d hiu: Random Forest khng d hiu v gii thch cho cc nh phn tch d liu do qu trnh xy dng m hnh phc tp.
    • Khng ph hp cho cc bi ton vi d liu dng chui hoc d liu thi gian: Random Forest khng ph hp cho cc bi ton phn loi v d on trn d liu dng chui hoc d liu thi gian do khng c tnh cht lin tc v tun t.
    • C th b overfitting nu s lng cy qu ln hoc cc tham s khng c iu chnh tt.
  1. K thut khai ph lut kt hp (dng fp-growth)
  • u im :
    • phc tp tnh ton thp hn so vi Apriori. FPGrowth s dng cu trc cy FP-Tree lu tr d liu, do khng cn phi duyt li tt c cc tp hp ph bin nh Apriori.
    • Hiu sut cao hn v khng phi duyt qua tt c cc tp ph bin.
    • C th tm kim cc tp ph bin vi h tr nh hn.
    • Khng yu cu lu tr tt c cc tp hp ph bin trong b nh, do ph hp vi cc tp d liu ln.
  • Nhc im FPGrowth:
    • Kt qu ca FPGrowth khng m bo chnh xc 100% v n s dng thut ton quy.
    • Thut ton c th dng li trc khi hon tt tm kim tt c cc tp ph bin, do c th b l mt s tp ph bin.
    • i vi cc tp d liu c t l lp li cao v s lng phn t ln, th FP-Tree c th tr nn rt ln, dn n tn nhiu b nh lu tr.
  1. K thut Artificial Neural Network
  • u im ca m hnh ANN:
    • Kh nng hc tp v tng hp thng tin.
    • X l d liu phi cu trc.
    • linh hot v kh nng ty chnh.
    • Kh nng d on v m hnh ha mi quan h phi tuyn.
  • Nhc im ca m hnh ANN:
    • i hi lng d liu ln.
    • Thi gian hun luyn lu.
    • D b overfitting.
    • phc tp v kh hiu.

CHƯƠNG 4: GIẢI THÍCH KẾT QUẢ KHAI PHÁ¶

  1. K thut hi quy tuyn tnh
    • Kt qu mean_squared_error l 1.1650467622619378 cho thy lch trung bnh gia gi tr d on v gi tr thc t ca m hnh trong vic d on nhit c th kh thp. iu ny cho thy m hnh ca chng ta c th ang hot ng tt trong vic d on nhit .
    • Kt qu R-squared (h s xc nh) l 0.9899303456016987, gn bng 1, cho thy m hnh c kh nng gii thch c hu ht s bin thin ca bin mc tiu (cm gic nhit) bng cc bin c trng nh nhit , m, tc gi v p sut. iu ny cng cho thy m hnh ca chng ta c kh nng kh cao trong vic d on nhit .
    • ng thi, kt qu ca vic d on trn mt bn ghi c th ca tp d liu khi dng Linear Regression l gn bng vi gi tr thc t.
  2. K thut SVM
    • Kt qu mean_squared_error l 1.1650467622619378 cho thy lch trung bnh gia gi tr d on v gi tr thc t ca m hnh trong vic d on nhit c th kh thp. iu ny cho thy m hnh SVM c kh nng d on chnh xc nhit c tnh.
    • Kt qu R-squared (h s xc nh) l 0.9899303456016987, gn bng 1, cho thy m hnh cng c kh nng gii thch c hu ht s bin thin ca bin mc tiu (cm gic nhit) bng cc bin c trng nh nhit , m, tc gi v p sut. iu ny cng cho thy m hnh SVM c kh nng gii thch c 98.99% s bin thin ca d liu nhit .
  3. K thut RandomForest
    • thut ton RandomForest phn loi tt hn trn cc tp d liu, chng ta cn tm v iu chnh cc tham s cho ph hp vi tng tp d liu. Cc tham s ph bin thng dng iu chnh l: n_estimators, criterion, max_depth, min_samples_split.
      • n_estimators: L s lng cy quyt nh trong rng. N cng ln th m hnh s cng n nh v chnh xc cng s ci thin. Tuy nhin, khi s lng cy qu ln, thi gian hun luyn s tng ng k m khng ci thin ng k chnh xc. Do , n cn c la chn mt cch cn thn t c s cn bng gia chnh xc v thi gian hun luyn.
      • criterion: L hm mc tiu c s dng o lng cht lng ca mt php phn chia. Trong thut ton Random Forest, hai hm mc tiu ph bin l Gini Impurity v Entropy. Hm mc tiu c s dng s nh hng n cch cy c to ra v chnh xc ca m hnh
      • max_depth: L su ti a ca cy quyt nh. Khi su ca cy qu ln, m hnh s d b overfitting. Nu gi tr max_depth qu nh, m hnh s d b underfitting. Do , gi tr max_depth cn c la chn mt cch cn thn t c s cn bng gia chnh xc v phc tp ca cy.
      • min_samples_split: L s lng mu ti thiu c yu cu phn chia mt nt thnh cc nt con. Nu mt nt c s lng mu t hn min_samples_split, n s khng c phn chia v tr thnh mt l ca cy. Tng gi tr min_samples_split s gim su ca cy v gip trnh tnh trng overfitting.
    • Ta c th s dng hm RandomizedSearchCV() t th vin sklearn tm ra cc tham s ph hp i vi tp d liu. V d i vi tp d liu Adult Income th cc tham s ph hp nht theo RandomizedSearchCV tm c l :
    • T cc gi tr ny lm tham s cho thut ton RandomForest bng vic s dng th vin sklearn ta thy Accuracy ln ti 0.86 l mt s tng i cao nh gi m hnh c hiu qu trong vic phn loi thu nhp ca ngi ln .
    • Bn cnh , trc quan hn v t l ng sai ca kt qu phn loi, ta c th xem confusion matrix
  4. K thut khai ph lut kt hp
    • Thc hin vic khai thc lut kt hp t tp d liu df bng thut ton FPGrowth. C th, cc tham s truyn vo l:
      • df: Tp d liu cha cc transaction c m t bi cc itemset.
      • min_support=0.2: Ngng support ti thiu ca cc itemset c coi l ph bin. Trong trng hp ny, ngng support c t l 0.2, c ngha l mt itemset ph bin nu n xut hin trong t nht 20% cc transaction.
      • use_colnames=True: S dng tn ct t tn cho cc item trong frequent itemsets.
    • Kt qu tr v l mt DataFrame cha cc frequent itemset ph bin vi support tng ng ca chng, cho thy c 90 frequent itemsets vi support ti thiu l 0.2.C th, cc ct ca DataFrame l support v itemsets. Ct support cha gi tr support ca tng itemset v ct itemsets cha cc itemset tng ng.
    • Cc itemset c a ra di dng frozenset, mt i tng khng th thay i c v khng c th t.
    • Tham s metric="confidence" v min_threshold=0.7, thut ton s dng ngng min_threshold lc cc lut kt hp m c tin cy (confidence) t nht l 0.7, da trn cc tp ph bin tm c bi FPGrowth. Cc lut kt hp c lu tr trong mt dataframe vi cc ct gm tp u vo, tp u ra, h tr (support), tin cy (confidence) v lift. Trong , h tr ca lut kt hp l h tr ca tp u vo v u ra, tin cy l t l gia h tr ca tp u vo v tp u ra, v lift l mt ch s nh gi mc ph thuc gia tp u vo v u ra, so vi tn sut xut hin ca tp u ra c lp.
  5. K thut Artificial Neural Network
    • Sau nhiu ln th nghim vi s n-ron tng lp v hm kch hot mi lp ta nhn thy:
      • u tin v hm kch hot :Hm relu l ph hp nht bi n p dng hm max(0,x), n gi li gi tr khng m v a cc gi tr m v 0. N a ra c hiu sut tt hn cc hm kch hot khc.Ngc li vi hm tanh v hm sigmoid thng dng cho cc bi ton phn loi. Suy ra khng ph hp vi nh ca nhm l d on. Vi hm kch hot linear th nhm nhn thy biu h thin s khc nhau tng t vi vic s dng m hnh linear. => Nhm s dng hm relu 2 trung gian.
      • Vi s lng n-ron trong cc lp n th trong qu trnh th nghim t 8, 16, 32, 64 th nhn thy cng tng s n rn th chnh xc ca m hnh cng cao => lp u tin s dng 64 n-ron v lp th 2 vi 32 n-rn, lp cui cng vi 1 n-ron cho ra bin lin tc ph hp vi bi ton d on ca nhm.Vi mse n nh l 0,4381 thp hn so vi 2 m hnh trc l linear regression v SVM.
  6. So snh gia SVM, Linear Regression v ANN
    • MSE v R-squared: Khi so snh MSE v R-squared gia m hnh SVM, Linear Regression v ANN trn tp d liu ny, ta thy SVM v Linear Regression c hai ch s kh gn nhau. iu ny cho thy c hai m hnh u c kh nng d on tng i tt vi tp d liu. Nhng i vi ANN( khi c s ln hun luyn ca m hnh l 10 ) th c MSE thp hn v R-squared th li cao hn, iu cho thy khi d on trn tp d liu ny th ANN tng i tt.
    • Thi gian d on: Thi gian d on ca m hnh liner regression nhanh hn ng k so vi m hnh SVM v ng thi c hai m hnh trn u nhanh hn so vi ANN. iu ny cho thy m hnh liner regression c hiu sut cao hn trong vic d on nhanh chng trn tp d liu ny.
    • Thi gian hun luyn: Tuy thi gian d on ca m hnh SVM nhanh hn so vi ANN v chm hn so vi Liner regression, nhng thi gian hun luyn ca m hnh SVM li lu nht. iu ny c th l do phng php ti u ha phc tp v tnh ton phc tp hn ca m hnh SVM. Vic hun luyn m hnh SVM yu cu thi gian nhiu hn tm ra cc siu mt phn chia ti u trong khng gian a chiu.
    • nh gi so vi 2 m hnh trc l Linear v SVM th ANN c hiu sut tt hn vi hin ti thm ch l tt hn na nu nhm c th tm c cc h s u vo tt hn. V thi gian th ANN s tn rt nhiu thi gian c th ti u tham s u vo ca model bng vic th nghim v iu chnh. thi gian lp li ti u hiu sut ca ANN cng mt rt nhiu thi gian so vi Linear v SVM.
